{"word":"γραμματεύς","slug":"γραμματεύς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>γραμματεύς, έως, ὁ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:γράμμα\">γράμμα</a></el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> of a high official in Ephesus, <b><i>secretary (of state), clerk</i> <a href='B:510 19:35'>Ac 19:35</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> of a specialist in Mosaic legal matters, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> in the gospels, <b><i>legal scholar, teacher of the law</i> <a href='B:470 7:29'>Mt 7:29</a>; <a href='B:480 1:22'>Mk 1:22</a>; <a href='B:530 1:20'>1 Cor 1:20</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <b><a href='B:470 13:52'>Mt 13:52</a>; <a href='B:470 23:34'>23:34</a>.</b> W. <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀρχιερεύς\">ἀρχιερεύς</a></el> <b><a href='B:470 2:4'>Mt 2:4</a>; <a href='B:480 11:18'>Mk 11:18</a>; <a href='B:490 19:47'>Lk 19:47</a></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ al.\">al.</a>; <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <el>Φαρισαῖοι</el> <b><a href='B:470 5:20'>Mt 5:20</a>; <a href='B:490 5:21'>Lk 5:21</a></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ al.\">al.</a> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:γράμμα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:γραπτός\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}